Class AddInventoryActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cs.swapmyride.AddInventoryActivity

  • public class AddInventoryActivity
extends java.lang.Object
    This class specifically works to add a vehicle to a user's inventory There is opportunity to input all information and a photo for the new vehicle, and then it is added to the inventory list.
